node.title: Rugby Championship updates: All Blacks defeat Springboks 35-20
node.description: The All Blacks have beaten South Africa 35-20 in their Rugby Championship match at Auckland's Mount Smart Stadium tonight. Follow all the action with a live blog from Jamie Wall.
